Business Description
Citius Pharmaceuticals (OTCQB: CTXR) is a specialty pharmaceutical company dedicated to the development and commercialization of therapeutic products for large and growing markets. Citius is currently advancing two proprietary product candidates, our Mino-Lok™ product and a hydrocortisone-lidocaine formulation. Citius believes the markets for its products are large and underserved by the current standard of care.
Company Info
Address:11 Commerce Drive, First FloorCranford, NJ 07016 
Telephone:908-967-6677
Email:info@citiuspharma.com
Industry Classifications
Sector:Healthcare
Industry:Drugs - Generic
SIC:8731 - Commercial Physical Research









Company Information

Profile


Presentations


Management Team


