Citius Pharmaceuticals Inc.


            
            Citius Pharmaceuticals, Inc. engages in the development and commercialization of therapeutic products. Its products include Mino-Lok and hydrocortisone-lidocaine. The company was founded on September 09, 2010 and is headquartered in Cranford, NJ.

            
